{"tid":878610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人無投資頭腦，做死一世窮人","createTime":"2018-10-27T09:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T11:30:20.000Z","uid":212996,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1625143d81ba12bb2710c001430eb2c89b943fce","tid":878610,"uid":212996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"窮人真係唔撚好生仔<br />\n窮人思想係生兒防老，等自己老咗有人養<br />\n屌你老母，你生完嗰仔但你唔投資落去<br />\n但你想嗰仔大過會養自己<br />\n係咪有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你連投資都唔做嘅時候<br />\n你竟然想回報<br />\n係咪食屎大<br />\n世界無免費午餐架<br />\n你要有回報嘅同時<br />\n請你首先要有投資<br />\n重點係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一個都養唔掂嘅時候<br />\n你仲要生多幾個<br />\non9思想無得教<br />\n窮人真係咪撚生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e9a05e09c9c1903468bb61bb438c606414ad69","tid":878610,"uid":179288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"咁你紮左未"},{"pid":"05be1ee9889e1b8098039575294999490eb2f78c","tid":878610,"uid":212996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2e9a05e09c9c1903468bb61bb438c606414ad69","tid":878610,"uid":179288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"咁你紮左未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"紮架嗱"},{"pid":"5e85863bee5f12bad38f8ea25b3def5afc176f4e","tid":878610,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:22:08.000Z","msg":"窮唔緊要<br />\n但咪撚蠢"},{"pid":"a986189094d68fa85380cedde6d7cd677ba3a3ec","tid":878610,"uid":212996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e85863bee5f12bad38f8ea25b3def5afc176f4e","tid":878610,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:22:08.000Z","msg":"窮唔緊要<br />\n但咪撚蠢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:23: